title: PhotoPlus &ndash; April 2012 (.PDF)
description: At last - a photography magazine which is 100% Canon, 100% for you! PhotoPlus is a new magazine for Canon DSLR users that will show you how to: take better shots, improve them on your PC, print and share them using the latest technology. Plus a video disk containing details step-by-step guides with every issue.With a subscription to PhotoPlus, we guarantee you'll be taking better photos, using Photoshop like a pro and making great prints to share, to frame or sell.
